column1: List out the low important events falling under strategy category starting from newest to oldest order.
column2: GET event FILTER event.categories eq strategy FILTER event.importance eq Low ORDERBY event.start desc

column1: What are the events I have in training category that ended last Friday ordered by start time newest to oldest?
column2: GET event FILTER event.categories eq Training FILTER event.end eq last Friday ORDERBY event.start desc

column1: Make a list of top 72 meetings under the feedback category and arrange them in descending order of their start time.
column2: GET event FILTER event.categories eq feedback ORDERBY event.start desc TOP 72

column1: Give me the meeting invitation received from Jude Dulemba in the status category and located at Darrel's office.
column2: GET event FILTER event.categories eq status FILTER event.location eq Darrel's office FILTER event.organizer eq Jude Dulemba

column1: List the events with attachments falling under products categories that started before last wednesday.
column2: GET event FILTER event.categories eq Products FILTER event.hasAttachments eq True FILTER event.start lt last Wednesday

column1: List out the events about differentiate service in simulation categories that started after last year.
column2: GET event FILTER event.categories eq simulation FILTER event.start gt last year SEARCH differentiate service

column1: List out the events without attachments falling under automation category taking place at lashawna's office.
column2: GET event FILTER event.categories eq automation FILTER event.hasAttachments eq False FILTER event.location eq Lashawna's office

column1: Provide me the events without attachments falling under 2001 category starting from oldest to newest order.
column2: GET event FILTER event.categories eq 2001 FILTER event.hasAttachments eq False ORDERBY event.start asc

column1: Which events of intranet categories starts after friday that ordered by start time in descending manner?
column2: GET event FILTER event.categories eq intranet FILTER event.start gt Friday ORDERBY event.start desc
